name: Papillion Scarf
description:
Our Papillion scarf features a vibrant kaleidoscope of butterflies to form an all over print of blues, greens and purples.
Limited edition scarf illustrated by Kelly Smith.
Finished with a hand rolled edge and our signature ‘L’ charm in one corner, in 100% silk chiffon it is super soft and drapes beautifully.
100% Silk. Dimensions 70*160cm.
Scarf comes packaged unboxed.

name: Lapin Scarf
description:
Our Lapin scarf is an escape to the garden full of peonies and bunnies, it's a whimsical world of peach tones and grassy greens. 
Limited edition scarf illustrated by Kelly Smith.
Finished with a hand rolled edge and our signature ‘L’ charm in one corner, in 100% silk chiffon it is super soft and drapes beautifully. 
100% Silk, Dimensions 70*160cm
Scarf comes packaged unboxed.
